songs.title: Why Can't We Live Together (Flush Edit)
songs.comments: Free download from Flush the new moniker of producer Vito De Luca who also goes by Aeroplane. This is a title he's using exclusively for his remixes and edits and he's kicking it off with this free download of Timmy Thomas' Why Can't We Live Together, a track also recently remixed by DJDS and probably best known for providing the sample for Hotline Bling - apparently it was also the first track that Vito De Luca sampled when he was 15 so some nice full circle action for you there. http://www.lagasta.com/timmy-thomas-why-cant-we-live-together-flush-edit/
